{"tid":1898673,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特告別傳統揭蓋手提改用iPhone 11","createTime":"2020-02-26T07:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T13:01:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"11d72c41b9edbfe6353169f3ab57867d529afa3c","tid":1898673,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）24 日接受國外媒體 CNBC 專訪時表示，武漢肺炎是「可怕的東西」，儘管新型冠狀病毒有全球大流行的威脅，但投資人不該因新聞消息而任意出售股票。此外，身為蘋果投資者的巴菲特在訪談中談到這家公司，也透露自己終於從使用已久的掀蓋手機，改為擁抱智慧型手機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於武漢肺炎疫情近日快速蔓延至義大利、伊朗、南韓等國家，感染人數激增，可能擾亂生產供應鏈並減緩全球經濟成長，本週一全球股市紛紛下跌，其中道瓊工業平均指數甚至狂瀉千逾點。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特接受 CNBC 專訪時指出，投資人應展望於公司 10 年至 20 年的時間並專注其盈利能力，具有前景的公司才能使股票表現良好，而且武漢肺炎疫情爆發並未改變他觀察長期前景。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特認為病毒是令人恐懼的東西，但長期投資人不應受每日的新聞頭條所影響。如果著眼現狀，股票所獲得的收益多於債券。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特所掌管波克夏海瑟威為蘋果最大股東，其持股比例達 5.4%、價值約 720 億美元（約台幣 2.2 兆元），但他先前使用的手機並非 iPhone，而是售價僅 20 美元的三星 Haven U320。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51GG27A6FjL._AC_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51GG27A6FjL._AC_.jpg&h=3cbb41d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如今巴菲特改用蘋果 iPhone 11 系列的手機，但未指明是該系列的哪一個機型。巴菲特表示這支 iPhone 不是他本人所購買的，而是包括蘋果執行長庫克（Tim Cook）在內的許多人合送的禮物。近年來庫克一直試圖說服他改用蘋果製造的產品，甚至在 2018 年受訪時表示，如果他需要的話，願意親自飛到波克夏總部的奧馬哈教他如何使用。<br />\n<br />\n即使巴菲特換了新手機，他仍嚴格使用 iPhone 而不沉迷。實際上他擁有一部 iPad，主要用於進行研究與查看股價。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2020/02/25/warren-buffett-calls-coronavirus-outbreak-scary-stuff-but-says-he-will-not-be-selling-stocks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2020%2F02%2F25%2Fwarren-buffett-calls-coronavirus-outbreak-scary-stuff-but-says-he-will-not-be-selling-stocks%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6XyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=110bde08\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2020/02/25/warren-buffett-calls-coronavirus-outbreak-scary-stuff-but-says-he-will-not-be-selling-stocks/</a>"},{"pid":"9c41aa51d95911f5cc7f4bed24b68be9a7a478c8","tid":1898673,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"巴佬i犬可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e31b42134d7a921d628fb15aca59b93b373f1c0","tid":1898673,"uid":166733,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"而是包括蘋果執行長庫克（Tim Cook）在內的許多人合送的禮物<br />\n<br />\n咩料夾份送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03024f0519f973e9ac03d201af55a74f23b6d202","tid":1898673,"uid":200328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e31b42134d7a921d628fb15aca59b93b373f1c0","tid":1898673,"uid":166733,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"而是包括蘋果執行長庫克（Tim Cook）在內的許多人合送的禮物<br />\n<br />\n咩料夾份送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"gay cook送部iphone 11仲要夾份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8d4c4328f3fb9a042ea24233d6a19c0c12c6d4","tid":1898673,"uid":180975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e31b42134d7a921d628fb15aca59b93b373f1c0","tid":1898673,"uid":166733,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"而是包括蘋果執行長庫克（Tim Cook）在內的許多人合送的禮物<br />\n<br />\n咩料夾份送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"小氣得滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f05a04aecc06b76ff4f918ea42c7ca2e9a4d24","tid":1898673,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c8d4c4328f3fb9a042ea24233d6a19c0c12c6d4","tid":1898673,"uid":180975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e